  "title": "Housekeeping Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervise housekeeping staff to ensure orderly housekeeping work</li>\n  <li>Maintenance of the general cleanliness of the hotel guest rooms and      public areas</li>\n  <li>Recommend procedures and policies for housekeeping operations to improve      standards and procedures</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum GCE 'O' Levels or SPM qualifications</li>\n  <li>Experience in Hotels/ Serviced residences will be an advantage,      with minimum 2 years of supervisory experience in housekeeping operations</li>\n</ul>",
